  <entry>
    <title>动态规划--不同路径</title>
    <link href="http://forxuyx.github.io/archives/634ae221.html"/>
    <id>http://forxuyx.github.io/archives/634ae221.html</id>
    <published>2021-01-04T02:42:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-19T16:33:49.638Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-题目描述"><a href="#1-题目描述" class="headerlink" title="1.题目描述"></a>1.题目描述</h1><p>一个机器人从一个m*n网格左上角向右下角移动，每次只能向下或向右移动，有多少种解法？</p><h1 id="2-问题分析"><a href="#2-问题分析" class="headerlink" title="2.问题分析"></a>2.问题分析</h1><p>初始值：</p><p>在边界上的dp每次只能走一步，即初始值均为1</p><p>dp[0] [i]和dp[j] [0]初始化均为1。</p><p>状态转移方程：</p><p>机器人到达一个点，只能由左边或者上边到达，故到达(i,j)点的走法为左边与上面走法之和，由此可得：</p><p>dp[i] [j] = dp[i-1] [j] + dp[i] [j-1] ;</p><h1 id="3-代码实现"><a href="#3-代码实现" class="headerlink" title="3.代码实现"></a>3.代码实现</h1><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">uniquePaths</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> m,<span class="keyword">int</span> n)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> dp[m][n];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;i &lt; m;i++)</span><br><span class="line">        dp[i][<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;i &lt; n;i++)</span><br><span class="line">        dp[<span class="number">0</span>][i] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>;i &lt; m;i++)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> j = <span class="number">1</span>;j &lt; n;j++)</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][j] = dp[i<span class="number">-1</span>][j] + dp[i][j<span class="number">-1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> dp[m<span class="number">-1</span>][n<span class="number">-1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="4-复杂度分析"><a href="#4-复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="4.复杂度分析"></a>4.复杂度分析</h1><p>时间复杂度：O(mn)</p><p>空间复杂度：O(mn)</p><h1 id="5-优化方案"><a href="#5-优化方案" class="headerlink" title="5.优化方案"></a>5.优化方案</h1><p>画出相应dp表格，我们可以发现dp[i] [j] 仅与第i行和第i-1行有关。由此可以得出新的状态转移方程：</p><p>dp[i] = dp[i-1] + dp[i]</p><p>且由于交换m和n不会对答案产生影响，因此时间复杂度为O(min(m,n))</p>]]></content>
    
    
